        <div class="section" id="overview">
            <div class="section-num">01</div>
            <h2>Overview</h2>
            <p>At JerseyGarage, we want you to love your purchase. If something isn't right, we've made our cancellation
                and refund process as simple as possible.</p>
            <div class="green-box">
                All eligible refunds are processed within <strong>5–7 business days</strong> of approval. Refunds go to
                your JerseyGarage Wallet or original payment method.
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="section" id="cancellation">
            <div class="section-num">02</div>
            <h2>Order Cancellation</h2>
            <p>You can cancel your order directly from your account under <strong>My Orders</strong>. Cancellations are
                allowed based on the current status of your order:</p>
            <table class="status-table">
                <thead>
                    <tr>
                        <th>Order Status</th>
                        <th>Cancellation Allowed?</th>
                    </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                    <tr>
                        <td>Placed / Confirmed</td>
                        <td><span class="badge badge-green">✓ Allowed</span></td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>Packed</td>
                        <td><span class="badge badge-green">✓ Allowed</span></td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>Shipped</td>
                        <td><span class="badge badge-yellow">⚠ Contact support</span></td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>Out for Delivery</td>
                        <td><span class="badge badge-red">✗ Not allowed</span></td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>Delivered</td>
                        <td><span class="badge badge-red">✗ Not allowed — raise return instead</span></td>
                    </tr>
                </tbody>
            </table>
            <p>You may cancel individual items in a multi-item order. If you cancel part of an order, only the cancelled
                item(s) will be refunded.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="section" id="cancel-window">
            <div class="section-num">03</div>
            <h2>Cancellation Window</h2>
            <p>We recommend cancelling as early as possible. Once an order is packed and handed to our courier partner,
                cancellation may not be guaranteed.</p>
            <div class="highlight-box">
                For time-sensitive cancellations, contact us immediately at <strong>support@jerseygarage.in</strong> or
                call <strong>+91 98765 43210</strong>.
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="section" id="returns">
            <div class="section-num">04</div>
            <h2>Returns</h2>
            <p>We accept returns within <strong>7 days of delivery</strong>. To be eligible, items must be:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Unused and unwashed</li>
                <li>In original packaging with tags attached</li>
                <li>Free from stains, damage, or signs of wear</li>
                <li>Accompanied by the original invoice</li>
            </ul>
            <p>Return requests must be raised through your account dashboard under <strong>My Orders → Request
                    Return</strong>. Our team will review the request within 2 business days.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="section" id="non-returnable">
            <div class="section-num">05</div>
            <h2>Non-Returnable Items</h2>
            <p>The following items are not eligible for return or refund:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Custom or personalized jerseys (name/number printing)</li>
                <li>Items marked as "Final Sale" or "Non-Returnable" on the product page</li>
                <li>Items that have been worn, washed, or altered</li>
                <li>Items returned without original packaging or tags</li>
                <li>Items damaged due to customer misuse</li>
            </ul>
            <div class="highlight-box">
                Exceptions apply for items that arrive defective, damaged, or incorrect — these are always eligible
                regardless of the above.
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="section" id="refund-process">
            <div class="section-num">06</div>
            <h2>Refund Process</h2>
            <p>Here's how a refund works after a cancellation or approved return:</p>
            <div class="timeline">
                <div class="timeline-step">
                    <div class="step-num">1</div>
                    <div class="step-body">
                        <h4>Request Raised</h4>
                        <p>You cancel the order or raise a return request from My Orders.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="timeline-step">
                    <div class="step-num">2</div>
                    <div class="step-body">
                        <h4>Review & Approval</h4>
                        <p>Our team reviews the request within 1–2 business days. For returns, we may ask for photos of
                            the item.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="timeline-step">
                    <div class="step-num">3</div>
                    <div class="step-body">
                        <h4>Pickup (Returns Only)</h4>
                        <p>A pickup is scheduled within 2–3 business days. Please keep the item packed and ready.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="timeline-step">
                    <div class="step-num">4</div>
                    <div class="step-body">
                        <h4>Refund Issued</h4>
                        <p>Once approved or item received, refund is processed within 5–7 business days.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="section" id="refund-timeline">
            <div class="section-num">07</div>
            <h2>Refund Timeline</h2>
            <table class="status-table">
                <thead>
                    <tr>
                        <th>Payment Method</th>
                        <th>Refund To</th>
                        <th>Timeline</th>
                    </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                    <tr>
                        <td>UPI / Net Banking</td>
                        <td>Original account</td>
                        <td>3–5 business days</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>Credit / Debit Card</td>
                        <td>Original card</td>
                        <td>5–7 business days</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>JerseyGarage Wallet</td>
                        <td>Wallet balance</td>
                        <td>Instant</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>Cash on Delivery</td>
                        <td>JerseyGarage Wallet</td>
                        <td>Within 24 hours of approval</td>
                    </tr>
                </tbody>
            </table>
            <p>Bank processing times may vary. JerseyGarage is not responsible for delays on the bank's end once the
                refund is initiated.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="section" id="wallet">
            <div class="section-num">08</div>
            <h2>Wallet Refunds</h2>
            <p>All refunds can be credited to your <strong>JerseyGarage Wallet</strong> for faster processing. Wallet
                balance can be used on future orders and never expires.</p>
            <div class="green-box">
                Choosing a wallet refund means you get your money back <strong>instantly</strong> upon approval — no
                waiting for bank processing.
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="section" id="cod">
            <div class="section-num">09</div>
            <h2>COD Orders</h2>
            <p>For Cash on Delivery orders that are cancelled or returned, refunds are issued exclusively to your
                <strong>JerseyGarage Wallet</strong>. Bank transfers are not available for COD refunds.</p>
            <p>The wallet amount can be used immediately for future purchases on JerseyGarage.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="section" id="damaged">
            <div class="section-num">10</div>
            <h2>Damaged or Wrong Items</h2>
            <p>If you received a damaged, defective, or incorrect item, please contact us within <strong>48 hours of
                    delivery</strong> with:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Your order ID</li>
                <li>Clear photos of the item and packaging</li>
                <li>A brief description of the issue</li>
            </ul>
            <p>We will arrange a free pickup and send a replacement or issue a full refund — your choice.</p>
            <div class="highlight-box">
                Do not return damaged or wrong items through the standard return flow. Contact support directly for
                faster resolution.
            </div>
        </div>

